      "created_at": "2016-12-16T15:31:36.784Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Ok tashi e degjova. Still do doja t’kishin gjetur dicka me poetike se ‘aq me ben’ … ose jam une shume parimore ne art. Nga e kenduara ne stil te leshuar m’u kujtua nje kenge qe e kam dashur shume e qe po perfitoj ta re-share: I make the same mistakes, always give in too much for little in return etc etc, vecse icik me ndryshe domethenia… jo aq me ben, por “shume ma ndjen”.<br>\n<div class=\"lazyYT\" data-youtube-id=\"Y2b7FyaynC0\" data-youtube-title=\"The Echo Friendly: Same Mistakes (OFFICIAL VIDEO)\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"270\" data-parameters=\"feature=oembed&amp;wmode=opaque\"></div></p>",
